CHARACTER NAMES

Choose a name that fits a post-apocalyptic Earth setting:

  - Use a single first name or a plausible full name.
  - Avoid joke names, slurs, and real-world celebrity names.
  - Avoid names that impersonate staff.

Use help rp title for an optional roleplay title displayed with your name.
Staff may require a rename for inappropriate names.

